Class DeviceEventsListOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.FilterOptions
      • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.ListOptions
        • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.devices.model.DeviceEventsListOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    @Preamble(description="Options to use when listing device events.")
public class DeviceEventsListOptions
extends ListOptions
    Options to use when listing device events.

    Note:

    • Filters:

      The list can be filtered server-side on some of the fields of a device events.

      The following filters are currently supported:

      Server-side filters
      Field Tag Filters
      not equal to equal to greater than less than like in not in
      stateChange TAG_FILTER_BY_STATE_CHANGE • •
      eventType TAG_FILTER_BY_EVENT_TYPE • • • •
      description TAG_FILTER_BY_DESCRIPTION • • • •
      dateTime TAG_FILTER_BY_DATE_TIME • • • •
      deviceId TAG_FILTER_BY_DEVICE_ID • • • •
      id TAG_FILTER_BY_ID • • • •
